name: Paleta Pals: Franken-Lime
description: A wise man once said, "You can be unhappy before you eat a paleta and you can be unhappy after you eat a paleta, but you're never unhappy WHILE you eat a paleta.‚Äù  What are paletas, you ask? They are a Mexican frozen treat.  Like popsicles, only better, paletas are made with fresh fruit, spices and sometimes creamy ingredients.
